{"tid":264742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[五桂山命案] 如果咁樣做可唔可以暪天過海?","createTime":"2017-05-31T05:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T08:49:45.000Z","uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0eb921326651750c0c887b10ef1e852763973e6","tid":264742,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"頭盔: 純學術討論<br />\n<br />\n假設殺人嘅係A同B  負責引開人嘅係C<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殺人之後 A whatsapp call C叫佢上番山會合<br />\n之後等C上山時 A同B負責係兇案現場負責嘅草叢行黎行去 整斷草叢d樹枝 制造有人行過嘅跡象<br />\n同時A同B whatsapp C 話「兩個鐘之後去m記食宵夜!」&lt;--假對話，後面再解釋<br />\n之後將A同B所有值錢野拎哂出黎<br />\n<br />\n同C會合之後 3個人可以夾口供 (因為人都死左 C點都會被charge謀殺 所以無得唔夾)<br />\n下一步係最重要嘅一步:<br />\nA同B各自用同一把刀桶傷自己(非要害) 扮暈左係現場<br />\nC就帶埋把刀同埋其他財物 行落山 落山途中埋左佢<br />\n<br />\nC落到山之後 刪除whatsapp call紀錄<br />\n兩個鐘之後 C再上山 去A同B同埋條屍嘅位<br />\nC報警<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------- 以下係ABC口供------------------<br />\nC有事落山(點都好啦 自己作)<br />\nAB同死者繼續行 <br />\nAB whatsapp C 約兩個鐘後食宵夜<br />\n之後AB同死者遇上ii 比人持刀威脅 交出財物<br />\n死者不服反抗 比ii桶死 AB嘗試幫拖 但都失敗受傷倒地 ii逃去無蹤<br />\nC係m記等左好耐都唔見人 怕有意外所以上山搵<br />\n見到3人倒地 所以報警<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熬兩刀可以唔洗坐終身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無咩地方會比差佬周到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56996a17a7ea33a6cab7d4ddc1c44bdac8a91bc2","tid":264742,"uid":1729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"你漏咗個D"},{"pid":"107eb4e1ef34b004330b96da76db593b521813c4","tid":264742,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你漏咗個D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你意思係比人引開果個?<br />\n咪照舊比C引開 whatever reason<br />\n唔影響架 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6016d9e1dabc11b16d5dd3ca16a5d105c8c45a26","tid":264742,"uid":57365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"真係覺得delete左既msg同call record check會唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac224154aa8091f541b825fb1e0e6eb67b78c7ca","tid":264742,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係覺得delete左既msg同call record check會唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢層真係唔清楚 但whatsapp call喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但就算係direct call都可以是旦up架 e.g. 好似漏左野 打去問下係咪果個人到"},{"pid":"bcfd3c91245a7c97c0a9fe989bd6ffda04acdef7","tid":264742,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"同A B落口供個陣對打劫既詳細經過一定會有出入同漏洞（因為事實上無發生過），然後會穿崩"},{"pid":"bb8c27e1fc0d74d01d6e76e7152528bf99dbaabd","tid":264742,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同A B落口供個陣對打劫既詳細經過一定會有出入同漏洞（因為事實上無發生過），然後會穿崩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢層就要睇夾得好無 同埋好唔好戲<br />\n或者話昏迷過唔太記得? (Post traumatic something like that?)"},{"pid":"0d94ba627829e97fe1b920424e540e7df4c887af","tid":264742,"uid":57365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:00:26.000Z","msg":"廢青比差佬兇兩兇咩都爆哂出黎搏減刑啦<br />\n又唔知另兩個會唔會篤灰出賣自己 以香港人性格幾大都為自己篤左灰"},{"pid":"e900ea506df98a19b2e9eddb623fbe4c986b1744","tid":264742,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係覺得delete左既msg同call record check會唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢層真係唔清楚 但whatsapp call喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但就算係direct call都可以是旦up架 e.g. 好似漏左野 打去問下係咪果個人到</blockquote><br />\n掩耳盜鈴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你真係當 人WHATSAPP